    codeExample: `<span class="text-yellow-400">---</span>
<span class="text-blue-400">import</span> <span class="text-green-400">MyReactComponent</span> <span class="text-blue-400">from</span> <span class="text-orange-300">'./MyReactComponent.jsx'</span><span class="text-slate-300">;</span>
<span class="text-yellow-400">---</span>

<span class="text-gray-500">&lt;!-- Static by default --&gt;</span>
